description: This is a compressed archive (609 MB, .rar format) of the Digital Elevation Model of the Western Indian Ocean. Its scope is from sea level to 90 m altitude in 1 m steps, covering all countries of the region. Individual tiles derived from the file are provided in the 'Layers' section of MASPAWIO.
keywords: coastal zone, Elevation, WIO, Africa, East Africa, Comoros, Kenya, Mauritius, Mayotte, Mozambique, Reunion, Seychelles, Somalia, United Republic of Tanzania, Southern Africa, South Africa
name: Coastal Digital Elevation Model (1 m resolution) - Western Indian Ocean
